{"tid":2182752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]有女手足要眾籌！","createTime":"2020-08-31T13:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T10:13:32.000Z","uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93e51150d45289e6937b2b08e27d3a60d2f875c3","tid":2182752,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:31:07.000Z","msg":"各位老公拆禮物🎁<br />\n✈️🥛【純愛杯】募資啟動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/chunse\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeczec.com%2Fprojects%2Fchunse&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=501681b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zeczec.com/projects/chunse</a><br />\n<br />\n「山有小口，彷彿若有光，便舍船，從口入。初極狹，纔通人；復行數十步，豁然開朗。」<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;陶淵明，《桃花源記》<br />\n <br />\n想像一個人，在結束一日勞動工作後，回到家已經無力再戰，連晚餐都想速食解決，生活欲振乏力，但就在這個時候，他發現了一個神奇之境，小小的通道彷彿見到了希望之光，進到入口，立刻被從未感受過的貼身安全感給包覆，才數十下，瞬間整個人身心都開闊了起來。<br />\n <br />\n這就是「純愛杯」的誕生宗旨，<br />\n要給你桃花源般的感受！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Avz9hrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvz9hrp.jpg&h=be76234d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31baeca5bcd8d24392b497df24ae40cd302a0748","tid":2182752,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee1d4e0b76f53d95b12837f5b1d5b6eb954955e2","tid":2182752,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T21:02:38.000Z","msg":"原來桃花源記係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244429e74b2a6726d4f38c598ea95ff54058cd0c","tid":2182752,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee1d4e0b76f53d95b12837f5b1d5b6eb954955e2","tid":2182752,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T21:02:38.000Z","msg":"原來桃花源記係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-